author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Another epic stream, and full of memories... A super classic played by the most beautiful necromancer princess. :_きゅん::_ハート:

Memorable highlights:

1:12:45 After defeating Hanma Brother, Rushia-hime went crazy and laughed a lot, even after defeating King Koopa.

1:13:23 Rushia-hime reads the Epilogue... Well... Definitively is english and not these "Dark Souls" stream's engrish. Rushia's english skill was improved again. 

2:04:39 In hard mode... Rushia-hime completed again the game... And again starts laughing maniacally. 

2:04:48 Rushia again read the english epilogue, but until "Push Button B"

And she ended game twice, first in normal mode and later in hard mode... :_ちょうちょ:

And about the form to defeat 8-4 King Koopa (Or Bowser on overseas) passing from below... The same tactic I made when passed 1-4 for first time despite the platform at top... :_サイリウム碧::_サイリウム紫:

But also, Rushia at least had more patience to defeat strong enemies as Hanma Bros. (Hammer Brothers) with stomping instead passing them from top or below.

author: Morales モラレスCarlos カルロス
text: そのレベルを通過するのは簡単ではなかったに違いないと思います。 もちろん、それは古いビデオゲームであり、古いゲームは印象的な難しさを持っているので。 しかし、練習すればそれをマスターすることができます。 このゲームに勝つために全力を尽くしてください。 あなたはこのゲームに勝つことができると確信しています。 まだあきらめないでください。 よく休む 👌👌🎆🎊🎆🎉🎆🌃🌃😉😉
